Public Class FishTips
    Private Sub BtnFishTips1_Click(sender As Object, e As EventArgs) Handles BtnFishTips1.Click
        MessageBox.Show("If you see your fish gasping at the surface with red or inflamed gills, they may have " & vbCrLf &
                        "ammonia poisoning. The water in their tank may appear murky, which is an indicator that " & vbCrLf &
                        "the water hasn’t been ‘cycled’. To treat this condition, test the water for ammonia and pH, " & vbCrLf &
                        "and check the water temperature. A 30 to 50 per cent water change is advised and you " & vbCrLf &
                        "need to repeat this within 24 hours as necessary." & vbCrLf &
                        "Clean the gravel in your fish tank with a gravel siphon and make sure you’re using high-" & vbCrLf &
                        "quality food that’s not out of date. To prevent this condition avoid overfeeding, " & vbCrLf &
                        "overcrowding and ensure your filtration system is working well.")
    End Sub

